{"tid":968881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聽過咩刻骨銘心嘅說話，你一世都會記住","createTime":"2019-01-04T15:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T17:57:14.000Z","uid":218088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2b99fea705b6c5e258db2ee3958a9bd111074209","tid":968881,"uid":218088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"首先係一句最後嘅叮囑：<br />\n爸爸患病，臨走前，叫我要好好照顧媽媽<br />\n<br />\n然後有兩句，係唔同嘅女仔對我講過嘅：<br />\n初戀同我講：太快樂如何招架　殘忍不好嗎<br />\nex同我講：我以前覺得可以同你行到最後，但依家已經唔咁覺得喇<br />\n<br />\n你哋呢？"},{"pid":"6febdc6c05d1cb40c51fdd70fac0484d11a25997","tid":968881,"uid":64374,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"576cabdcd35b2f6cc4619fdd933fd16a3be1fea8","tid":968881,"uid":431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"初戀同我講：太快樂如何招架　殘忍不好嗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d459c3bb3ddc5bbe9c51791b3a5d8dc140bd835","tid":968881,"uid":220174,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"好耐之前同家姐鬧交，搞到警察上黎調停。<br />\n<br />\n警察哥哥同我講:<br />\n成屋得你一個男仔，你要生性啲，堅強啲去撐起頭家。得你一個有能力去保護呢班女人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEx:我發現你從來都無了解過我。"},{"pid":"4e68d26821126cc5a541beebba1aa88f8c27701f","tid":968881,"uid":87582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"時間唔岩 點我地都一齊唔到"},{"pid":"38a6e8624a5bde74108697c3ac8576e1b3700aa4","tid":968881,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"ex:I&rsquo;m yours<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b2a48df78b2adddb0ece33c51681918cfa8a56","tid":968881,"uid":67908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b4d9ebf939d24322d5ec318823de1f1c50a8de","tid":968881,"uid":147532,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"只要做個善良嘅人就夠，其他野唔重要"},{"pid":"d52994bb3d1283aa29a85e950046004edb9a1253","tid":968881,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:53:05.000Z","msg":"拍咗兩年，分咗手又兩年，由我遇上佢開始總共係四年。<br />\n<br />\n就係尋晚，係我二十歲生日，我終於忍唔住問咗佢呢條收埋係我心入面好耐嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n我：『如果我重新再追你一次，我仲會唔會有機會？』<br />\n<br />\n佢：『算啦&hellip;&hellip;』<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd7411cc43a3d4385d707cdfefc7471dbf08d5e","tid":968881,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6febdc6c05d1cb40c51fdd70fac0484d11a25997","tid":968881,"uid":64374,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"屈機狗D廢話你都當係至理名言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90cd983b0fc4043fb8ed0810a9539d45559f0c6","tid":968881,"uid":191988,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:03:15.000Z","msg":"男朋友同我講<br />\n<br />\n「人生有好多野無得揀<br />\n但女朋友係我揀既無人逼我<br />\n我一定會努力都要同你走到最後。」<br />\n<br />\n哩句說話係拍拖初期講<br />\n個陣只係笑下算<br />\n宜家就快走過第6個年頭<br />\n<br />\n諗番咁多年既相處<br />\n再回想哩句說話<br />\n佢真係講得出做得到<br />\n真男人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c545250422ab4f937196d593a3907585c4073b6d","tid":968881,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e68d26821126cc5a541beebba1aa88f8c27701f","tid":968881,"uid":87582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"時間唔岩 點我地都一齊唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5345c25ea83c430c30e1c52a8a92e9331bee5ee8","tid":968881,"uid":162295,"like":0,"dislike":